[[File:Mingula.jpg|thumb|250px|''Mingula'', a ''ZZ''-class freighter]]
The '''''ZZ''-class freighter''' was a [[Freighter/Legends|freighter]] of an unknown design. It had a long and thin shape. Despite its great size, the class could be operated by a crew of as few as four.

''[[Mingula]]'' was a ''ZZ''-class freighter chartered to transport the remains of [[Volpau]], a cousin of [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]], to [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] to undergo ritual incineration, along with his many possessions. It was discovered drifting in open space by [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] after the crew was killed by an infestation of [[Ubuugan fleshborer]]s in [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]]; to escape the creatures, Fett was forced to ignite the vessel's fuel cells and destroy it.

